<h2>Create a new resource type</h2>
<form class="form" name="resourceForm">
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="resource_id">Resource Type ID</label>
        <small>The ID of the resource type</small>
        <input
            id="resource_id"
            autofocus="autofocus"
            pattern="[a-z][a-z_]*[a-z]"
            title="Only lowercase characters with underscores in between."
            name="yourturn_resource_id"
            required="required"
            placeholder="sales_order"
            type="text" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="resource_name">Resource Type Name</label>
        <small>The name of the resource type</small>
        <input
            id="resource_name"
            name="yourturn_resource_name"
            required="required"
            placeholder="Sales Order"
            type="text" />
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label>Resource Owner</label>
        <small>Who owns the resource? Who can grant access to the resource? For now itâ€™s okay to not have any resource owner.</small>
        <label for="employees">
            <input
                name="yourturn_resource_owner_employee"
                id="employees"
                type="checkbox" /> Employees
        </label>
        <label for="applications">
            <input
                name="yourturn_resource_owner_application"
                id="applications"
                type="checkbox" /> Applications
        </label>
        <label class="form-disabled" for="customer">
            <input
                disabled="disabled"
                name="yourturn_resource_owner_customer"
                id="customers"
                type="checkbox" /> Customers (available later this year)
        </label>
        <label class="form-disabled" for="brands">
            <input
                disabled="disabled"
                name="yourturn_resource_owner_brands"
                id="brands"
                type="checkbox" /> Brands (available later this year)
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="resource_description">Resource Type Description</label>
        <small>An elaborate description with examples of what kind of data this resource type includes. You can use <a data-external href="http://www.unexpected-vortices.com/sw/rippledoc/quick-markdown-example.html">Markdown</a>.</small>
        <textarea
            id="resource_description"
            name="yourturn_resource_description"
            cols="30"
            rows="10"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group">
        <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fa fa-save"></i> Save
        </button>
    </div>
</form>